{"tid":1976584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］下午觀塘有手足被捕 黑警沙展：你痴X左 入新屋嶺啦","createTime":"2020-04-17T10:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T12:02:34.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"06ac0bfe6852af65554f14aedc14ee35a18cab8c","tid":1976584,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，觀塘同仁街近港鐵站A出口位置，有數名男子在民政事務處壁報板（即觀塘連儂牆）上張貼文宣，內容為變態辣椒Rebel Pepper所畫的「病毒之王習近平」，諷刺國家主席習近平及武漢肺炎疫情。突然，有衝鋒車駛到現場，警員下車後圍捕這批男子，行動隨即引起市民圍觀以及用手機拍攝。其間，一名警長失控辱罵圍觀市民，令市民感到相當不滿。未幾大批警員到場增援，並將其中數名圍觀市民帶到防線後調查，這名警長得勢不饒人，不斷挑釁其中一名被調查市民，例如「收皮啦」、「傻X咗呀」、「曱甴」、「望住我啊」、「入新屋嶺」等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在場有電訊sales不恥警方的行上前聲援，亦遭對方截查，其後多架衝鋒車到場，大約有20名警員在場戒備，氣氛一度緊張。至下午4時許，被查市民和張貼文宣男子均被警員帶返警署，在場警員用黑色膠袋遮蔽文宣後，亦陸續收隊離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200417/I3AQYNLZWGSY7HKTCXDQ6UZHV4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200417%2FI3AQYNLZWGSY7HKTCXDQ6UZHV4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9yWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=823ce8ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200417%2FI3AQYNLZWGSY7HKTCXDQ6UZHV4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d72d2967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200417/I3AQYNLZWGSY7HKTCXDQ6UZHV4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"0c308eb244c329c4005fe8d7be062cfe4f51e3f5","tid":1976584,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"市民圍觀以及用手機拍攝.<br />\n<br />\n算尻數啦, 革命, 革你老尾<img src=\"/asset